column1: ModelResponse(parts=[TextPart(content='{\n  ""sparql_query"": ""PREFIX ns1: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>\\nPREFIX ns2: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>\\nPREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>\\nPREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>\\n\\nSELECT DISTINCT ?propLabel ?alcEndpoint ?mpcEndpoint WHERE {\\n  # zones and their properties\\n  ?zone a ns1:Zone .\\n  ?zone ns1:hasProperty ?prop .\\n  ?prop rdfs:label ?propLabel .\\n  \\n  # exclude writable properties (no explicit true flag)\\n  FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?prop ns2:writable true }\\n\\n  # optional external reference that holds the ALC and MPC endpoints\\n  OPTIONAL {\\n    ?prop ns1:hasExternalReference ?extRef .\\n    ?extRef ns2:endpoint ?alcEndpoint .\\n    ?extRef ns2:mpc_db_name ?mpcEndpoint .\\n    # make sure the external reference is marked as nonâ€‘writable (most are stored as the string \\""False\\"")\\n    FILTER ( ?extRef ns2:writable \\""False\\""^^xsd:string || !BOUND(?extRef) )\\n  }\\n}\\nORDER BY ?propLabel""\n}', part_kind='text')], model_name='hosted_vllm/hosted_vllm/gpt-oss-120b', timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 22, 3, 40, 2, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), kind='response')

ModelResponse(parts=[TextPart(content='{\n  ""sparql_query"": ""PREFIX s223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>\\nPREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>\\nPREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>\\n\\nSELECT ?ahu ?property ?endpoint\\nWHERE {\\n  # Identify each Air Handling Unit (RTU)\\n  ?ahu a s223:AirHandlingUnit .\\n  # Get its properties (observable/actuatable)\\n  ?ahu s223:hasProperty ?property .\\n  # The property should have an external reference\\n  ?property s223:hasExternalReference ?extRef .\\n  # External reference must be nonâ€‘writable\\n  ?extRef brick:writable false .\\n  # Retrieve the endpoint URI/value\\n  ?extRef brick:endpoint ?endpoint .\\n  # Keep only ALC or MPC endpoints (caseâ€‘insensitive match)\\n  FILTER regex(str(?endpoint), \\""ALC|MPC\\"", \\""i\\"")\\n}\\nORDER BY ?ahu ?property""\n}', part_kind='text')], model_name='hosted_vllm/hosted_vllm/gpt-oss-120b', timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 22, 3, 43, 3, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), kind='response')
